  %p 1.  The name of the domain from which you access the Internet
  %p 2.  The date and time you access our site
  %p 3.  The Internet address of the website you used to link directly to our site.
  %p 4.  Which pages you visit
  %p 5.  The duration of each visit
  %p 6.  Any actions taken while on the site
